data.description: Beautifully appointed family home in the desirable Blain Park neighborhood. Enter through the custom DBL doors to a landing with lovely hard wood floors and step down into a formal DR, or formal Living room. Then proceed to the den with a huge travertine tile fireplace with faux log for safe and cozy ambiance. It Features beautiful, upgraded granite in kitchen and 2 baths. Kitchen and baths downstairs  cabinets are custom, the sinks are hammered copper. There are chandeliers, surround sound, custom crown molding, and lovely fans throughout the home. Then step outside to the outdoor kitchen BBQ and refreshing pool! The lot is just over 14000 Sq. Ft. of entertaining space! RV parking and gates with extra wide driveway for parking and all your riding toys. The roof is just 7 years, and 2 new A/C'S installed in 2020/21. Too much to list! Come and experience this beautiful home. Make your appointment today!
